      "review_title": "Great game but one small issue",
      "review_description": "I love Magnetic Me it is a great game. When I first joined I was greeted by a very nice admin and he showed me and a group of people how to play the game. I haven’t had the time yet to fully enjoy this amazing game because of timing. Also the movement is amazing but I feel like you should be able to move with just your hands for the ground.\nMy only big problem is that your hand has to be very close to the tablet for it to work and there is no free customization (that I have found).\nOtherwise great game 5/5 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️",
